{"tid":950921,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Pro Club 招神龍助陣，備戰ACL","createTime":"2018-12-22T02:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T09:12:59.000Z","uid":70926,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86f6d0584e3555e0dcc95ff24d89984c13bebc8c","tid":950921,"uid":70926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:15:58.000Z","msg":"球隊名稱：Easy D1<br />\n陣型：4231<br />\n開波時間：<br />\n10:00-1:00 （一至五） <br />\n不定（六/日）<br />\n<br />\n本屆首次參加HKVPL，有幸獲取ACL資格<br />\n<br />\n現招一神龍助陣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（其實勁過電腦就得）<br />\n<br />\n雖然我地冇球星，比賽經驗亦都唔多，但注重合作、紀律性同埋戰術既執行力，良好氣氛，希望大家可以一齊進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有意加我tg：lung94628 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429af03c647a9dbb695a880d39de628623b296d3","tid":950921,"uid":56583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"Pro club界李斯特城<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd3b7a80a6e48a7f5ce519539d64e4a3f3b5ab0","tid":950921,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"Lung爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836e89a4e2b8c9282a43269a7c9d25a5f59596ed","tid":950921,"uid":70926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429af03c647a9dbb695a880d39de628623b296d3","tid":950921,"uid":56583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"Pro club界李斯特城<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo